						               													<description>With the introduction of CPOP's Retrowave Collection, 1944: Combat Shock has been remastered, restored and resurrected. Return to the fields of battle. Return to the hell of World War II.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can now enjoy the game originally published in 2013, with minor changes, including updates and grammatical alterations. 1944: Combat Shock returns in an updated revision.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Combat Shock, players construct either platoons or full companies and engage in brutally quick and easy to play skirmishes across the battlefields of World War II. Miniatures in 15mm scale are mounted on bases to represent teams and scenarios determine the kind of battles fought. Players can play small-scale skirmishes on tabletops of 2 by 2 feet, to epic-scale conflicts on 4 by 4 foot tabletops.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This digital rulebook is in PDF format and includes basic and advanced rules, as well as several playable scenarios, rules for platoon and company construction, force lists for Nazi Germany, the Soviet Union, the United States of America and Great Britain. Also included are rules for battle conditions and more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
